    "description": {
      "value": "<p><strong>Scroll of Fly</strong> (Level 3 Transmutation)</p><p>You touch a willing creature. The target gains a flying speed of 60 feet for the duration. When the spell ends, the target falls if it is still aloft, unless it can stop the fall.</p><p><em>When you cast this spell using a spell slot of 4th level or higher, you can target one additional creature for each slot level above 3rd.</em></p><p><strong>Components:</strong> V, S, M (A wing feather from any bird.)</p><p><strong>Casting Time:</strong> 1 action | <strong>Range:</strong> Touch | <strong>Duration:</strong> Up to 10 minutes (Concentration)</p><p><em>Classes: Sorcerer, Warlock, Wizard</em></p>",
